Telefon aslında 2023 yılının Kasım ayında Çin'e özel olarak çıkan Redmi K70'in global versiyonu. Yani yeni bir cihaz olmasına rağmen o kadar da yeni olmadığını söyleyeyim.

Normal kullanımda şu sıcaklarda bile bir ısınma görmedim. Batarya sıcaklığı 40 derecenin üstünü görmüyor. Squad Busters gibi basit bir oyunda 40 derece civarında seyrederken Warzone gibi ağır bir oyun oynadığınızda ise 45 dereceleri görüyor. Bu piyasada araştırdığım bütün telefonlarda böyle. Çünkü hem telefonlar güçlü hem de oyunlar çok ağır.

Yazılımında herhangi bir takılma vs. yok ki bu durum beni daha önceden 3 Xiaomi cihaz daha kullanmış biri olarak epey şaşırttı. Çünkü yazılım konusunda çokça şikayet edilen bir marka bildiğiniz üzere.

Ekranı oldukça kaliteli. Samsung S23 Ultra ile yan yana koyduğumda gözüme biraz daha iyi geldi ama eşit diyebilirim.

Bataryası %0-100 arasını ortalama 25-30 dakikada tamamlıyor. Firmanın iddia ettiği gibi normal şartlar altında 19 dakikada dolum söz konusu değil ama ciddi bir fark da yok. Çok tatmin ettiğini söyleyebilirim. Ayrıca bataryası normal uygulamaların yoğun kullanımında bile bir günü çok rahat çıkartıyor. Ağır oyunlar oynandığında bir günü çıkarabileceğini zannetmiyorum ama zaten 25-30 dakikada doluyor olması bunu bir sorun olmaktan çıkarıyor benim gözümde. 120w max. şarj etme modunda batarya 42-45 derecelere ulaşıyor. Its unique , price is affordable, i dont mind not having 3 lens camera i have the most unique pink color of iphone 2021💞📱 the pictures are great by the way even if its not 3 lens 😄 💞💞💞💞💞'}, {'Reviewer': 'ぽこニャン2号', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Japan on 1 May 2022', 'Review': '11プロが壊れたので13にしようと思いました。どうせなら
ポイントも増えるとアマゾンで買いましたが。
欲しい色は256Gでした。よく見たら128Gはピンクしか

ランニングコストを考えれば、安心して使えて、トータルで
コスパがいい。'}, {'Reviewer': 'amyy', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Japan on 19 April 2022', 'Review': 'ワイモバイルSIMとの抱き合わせキャンペーンで購入しました。いつもAmazonを使いかつワイモバイルSIMを考えているなら、2万ポイント還元はベストチョイスだと思います。
購入後に来た専用申し込みURLがのっているメールにある「エントリーコード」とは、いつ使うのか？使う時があるのか？
キャンペーンのページを見てもよく分からなかったので、Amazonサポートに電話して聞きました。かなり長く待たされた後の答え→「専用URLの申し込みページから申し込めば“2万円キャンペーン”は適用になります。」とのこと。
それでは、何のためにエントリーコードが記載されているのか？･･･という素朴な疑問は横に置いて、申し込みを完了させました。

iPhone13は軽くてとても満足しています。11からの変更ですが、マスク付き顔認証がほしかったので。コツはあるけど、使ってみてやはり便利でした。'}]

5. Camera: The camera quality on the iPhone 14 Plus is exceptional. The photos and videos captured are rich in detail and clarity. The advanced camera features and modes provide ample opportunities for creativity.

6. App Ecosystem: The App Store offers a vast selection of high-quality apps that enhance the iPhone experience. I found all my favorite Android apps and discovered some excellent iOS exclusives.

7. Privacy and Security: Apple's commitment to user privacy and security is evident. Features like App Tracking Transparency and Face ID add an extra layer of protection.

8. Battery Life: The battery life on the iPhone 14 Plus is impressive. I can comfortably go through a day of heavy usage without worrying about running out of power.

In conclusion, my transition from Android to the iPhone 14 Plus has been a positive one. reviews:
[{'Reviewer': 'Darvy Guerrero', 'Rating': '1.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in the United States on 27 June 2024', 'Review': 'Phone’s camera is not working'}, {'Reviewer': 'Cliente Amazon', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Spain on 30 August 2024', 'Review': 'Llevo meses ya con el tele y debo decir que estoy totalmente satisfecho con él.
Va como un tiro, no me ha dado ni un problema y la cámara es una maravilla.
En cuanto a rendimiento, ninguna queja. Lo mueve todo sin problemas, incluso con muchas aplicaciones abiertas.
De memoria va más que sobrado, así que el hecho de no tener tarjeta de ampliación no me afecta.
La cámara, como he dicho, es una pasada. Gran resolución, muy configurable y con un zoom alucinante. El estabilizador funciona de maravilla también.
El sonido es muy bueno también, con el dolby.
Las únicas pegas que le encuentro son que la vibración es muy suave y a veces no me entero cuando llega algo y está en ese modo, que las notificaciones no suenan muy fuerte, (aunque el tono de llamada sí), y que al conectado al PC, como todos los realme, se pone a buscar fotos de forma automática y tardas un poco en poder manejarte entre las carpetas.
Sin tres pujada, pero por lo demás, estoy encantado con el teléfono.'}, {'Reviewer': 'Salex', 'Rating': '4.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Italy on 24 July 2024', 'Review': "Ho provato questo smartphone poiché era molto apprezzato nella fascia di prezzo 300/400 Euro, che è quella che mi intèressa.
Ecco le mie impressioni dopo alcuni giorni di utilizzo:

**Design e Costruzione:**
Il telefono si presenta bene e solido. Esteticamente, non amo il comparto fotografico così invadente al centro, ma sono solo gusti personali.

**Autonomia:**
Arrivando da un Samsung S23 che non mi permetteva di terminare la giornata con una sola carica, questo device è una piacevole sorpresa. Utilizzandolo intensamente, riesce a coprire un'intera giornata senza problemi. Acceso dalle 8 di mattina, arriva facilmente alle 23 con ancora un 15-20% di carica residua e quasi 6 ore di schermo attivo.

**Prestazioni:**
La fluidità è discreta e non presenta impuntamenti significativi. Le prestazioni generali sono adeguate per la fascia di prezzo.

**Fotocamera:**
Il comparto fotografico sa il fatto suo, anche nelle foto con scarsa illuminazione. Sebbene non sia il top di gamma, le foto risultano comunque di buona qualità per un telefono di questa fascia.

**Connettività:**
Ottimo il segnale telefonico; il dispositivo prende molto bene anche in posti dove i miei precedenti device stentavano a restare connessi.

**Display:**
Il display è ottimo anche alla luce del sole, rendendo facile l'utilizzo all'aperto.

**Ricarica:**
Molto comoda la ricarica ultra veloce, che in meno di un'ora abbondante porta la batteria al 100%.

**Punti di Critica:**
Non sarebbe stato male se fosse stato un po' più leggero e magari più sottile, ma non si può avere tutto. L'unico vero problema riscontrato è stato con il vivavoce: molti amici mi hanno detto che mi sentivano male, anche con il telefono vicino alla bocca.

**Conclusioni:**
Detto questo, se l'estetica delle fotocamere vi piace, è un telefono davvero tuttofare. Per la fascia di prezzo, offre un ottimo rapporto qualità-prezzo e soddisfa le esigenze quotidiane con efficacia.

Title: Apple iPhone 15 (128 GB) - Black
Description:
About this item
DYNAMIC ISLAND COMES TO IPHONE 15 — Dynamic Island bubbles up alerts and Live Activities — so you don’t miss them while you’re doing something else. You can see who’s calling, check your flight status and so much more.
NNOVATIVE DESIGN — iPhone 15 features a durable colour-infused glass and aluminium design. It’s splash, water and dust resistant.1 The Ceramic Shield front is super-tough. And the 6.7 Super Retina XDR display2 is up to 2x brighter in the sun compared to iPhone 14.
48MP MAIN CAMERA WITH 2X TELEPHOTO — The 48MP Main camera shoots in super high resolution. So it’s easier than ever to take standout photos with amazing detail. The 2x optical-quality Telephoto lets you frame the perfect close-up.
NEXT-GENERATION PORTRAITS — Capture portraits with dramatically more detail and colour. Just tap to shift the focus between subjects — even after you take the shot.
POWERHOUSE A16 BIONIC CHIP — The superfast chip powers advanced features like computational photography, fluid Dynamic Island transitions and Voice Isolation for phone calls. And A16 Bionic is incredibly efficient to help deliver great all-day battery life.
USB-C CONNECTIVITY — The USB-C connector lets you charge your Mac or iPad with the same cable you use to charge iPhone 15. You can even use iPhone 15 to charge Apple Watch or AirPods.
VITAL SAFETY FEATURES — If you need emergency services and you don’t have mobile service or Wi-Fi, you can use Emergency SOS via satellite.4 With Crash Detection, iPhone can detect a serious car crash and call for help if you can’t.

reviews:
[{'Reviewer': 'Shaurya', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in India on 1 August 2024', 'Review': 'Yeh phone sach mein ek all-rounder hai. Performance top-notch hai aur SUPERVOOC charging se battery jaldi full charge ho jaati hai, aur poora din chalti hai bina kisi problem ke. Camera quality zabardast hai, photos clear aur vibrant aati hain, aur night mode bhi kamaal ka hai. Storage capacity bhi kaafi achi hai, saare photos, videos, aur apps easily store ho jaate hain. Definitely worth buying!'}, {'Reviewer': 'Pathikrit Sur', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in India on 23 July 2024', 'Review': "I am using this mobile for two days now and I am much satisfied with it. I live in outskirts and I don't get 5g inside the house (in the extreme end of the rooms with realme 9i 5g, mind that I get full 5g in the drawing room and other rooms except the room which is very much inside) so my primary purpose was 5g inside the house, which I am getting now with oppo a3 pro. I don't do heavy gaming rather some light games and they are running fine. Below I am pointing the pros and cons for others to find helpful:
Pros :
1) 5g network : Firstly in outskirts of west bengal you will never get jio, or voda so try airtel and airtel only. I am getting 24 hours 5g even in burrow holes. So, you will get airtel 5g in this phone.
2) Battery : Decent battery and even if you play mild games it must serve you one day.
3) Design : It may not matter to many but the design is very eye-catching.
4) Camera : Decent. I will give 3/5. I am not a fan of camera.
5) Sound - Very loud sound.
6) Very sturdy and splash proof ip 54 rating.

Cons :
1) Price - Most important thing is it very very overpriced. Market price is ₹21000. Which is very costly if you ask me. I got it at ₹17k but still it is not worth it, for many people as the features are not much to speak of.
2) Processor is not up to the mark as per pricing. Heavy gaming will lag and may be even heat up (I didn't test it)
3) Charger is not 45W - Even though the charger says 45W charging but, when I checked the adapter it says 5V=2A or 9V=4.1A which means if you have low voltage it will charge slow and even if it is okay it is not 45w, but something around 40W. Charged 20% to 100% in 1hour 50 minutes. There is no logo on the adapter or cord
4) Hybrid Sim Slot - I checked in online site and did not know (my mistake though but still) so you can either have two Sims or one sim and a sd card (1tb expandable).

Verdict - If you can afford 2k more and don't have any reservations about better network then go for iqoo z9. It has lesser 5g bands so I bought this or else iqoo z9 is much better than this, go for it.

reviews:
[{'Reviewer': 'Amazon Customer', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Canada on 20 January 2024', 'Review': 'This phone is and excellent phone. La única diferencia destacable en contra del 7pro además del tamaño, es la falta del telefoto y la diferencia de la pantalla, aunque la verdad para el usuario común la diferencia entre el 2K y el FHD+ es casi imperceptible en una pantalla tan pequeña como lo son las de los smartphones, los 90 hercios y los 120 del pro igual no representan una gran diferencia, así que las únicas grandes adiciones en realidad en contraparte del pro son el tamaño y el telefoto, que dependiendo del usuario que seas el telefoto casi no se usa. Así que si buscas un teléfono compacto y fácil de usar a una mano, y no echas en falta el telefoto, es una excelente opción ante su hermano mayor, por casi la mitad del precio'}, {'Reviewer': 'Roger', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Singapore on 27 October 2022', 'Review': 'Brought to replace old pixel. Hay cosas que si extraño de los galaxy como la pantalla lateral y spen, pero hasta ahorita me a gustado bastante hasta estoy pensando en comprar el pixel 8 o 9 el síguete año .
Lo fui a probar a un concierto y la verdad no me defraudó .'}, {'Reviewer': 'Yudi Narine', 'Rating': '5.0 ', 'Date': 'Reviewed in Canada on 7 April 2023', 'Review': "Used to have a Samsung S7 before. Even though that phone is very old, the Pixel 7 is a massive improvement in both the camera and efficiency. It has probably the best phone camera I've ever used. I regret not getting the Pixel 7 Pro to get the telephoto camera.

It has so many Quality-of-Life changes built into the phone that I would've never thought about. Here's some examples:
- It has adaptive charging, which means it calculates the perfect rate to charge the phone so that it can charge to 100% before your next alarm will trigger
- Even though adaptive charging is on by default, it has the option to disable it temporarily so that you can do a quick fast charge if you're in a rush
- It tells you up until what time the phone will last until with the charge left on it
- When you copy something, it has a shortcut button to paste it immediately instead of having to hold down on the screen
- Taking a screenshot and cropping is so much faster

There's a bunch more QoL changes that I can't think of off the top of my head. Also, I realize some of these features might've been developed in earlier models, but it's still nice to have.
